Bronze LED 14 Inch Gooseneck Barn Light 42W 4027Lm 5000K Daylight - LED Outdoor Light Fixture - Dusk to Dawn Photocell Included - Swivel Head, IP65 Wet Location

DESIGN & OPTIONS. LED GOOSENECK LIGHT WITH PHOTOCELL has a traditional design with an adjustable head for more directional lighting. The durable die-cast aluminum construction provides extra resistance against rust and corrosion, quickens the heat dissipation process and extends the fixture's life. The built-in dusk-to-dawn photocell automatically turns the fixture on/off depending on the time of day. It comes with 120-277V, a 3000K, 4000K or 5000K color temperature and a BRONZE or WHITE finish.

INSTALLATION. These lights mount to a standard junction box. The shade is secured at a knuckle that can be adjusted to the desired angle. All mounting hardware included. Refer to installation instructions for more detailed steps.

APPLICATION. LED GOOSENECK LIGHT WITH PHOTOCELL is suitable for both indoor and outdoor applications such as gardens, patios, driveways, garages, barns, loading areas, building exteriors, parking lots, streets, storefronts, or anywhere else lighting is needed. These lights are Wet location rated and can operate in temperatures between -40°+131°F (-40°+55°С), allowing them to be utilized in a wide variety of applications and climates.

ENERGY SAVINGS & EFFICIENCY. Replacing an incandescent fixture with LED GOOSENECK LIGHT WITH PHOTOCELL can save you 8 times as much on your current energy costs. With a lifespan of 50,000 hours, these fixtures are made to last decades under normal operation! This fixture will save you a significant amount of money in its lifetime.

CERTIFICATION & WARRANTY. Buy with confidence: ASD provides a 5-year warranty along with ETL and ENERGY STAR certifications to guarantee top-quality products and safety!
